<div class="app-card-container">
	<div class="card">
		<h1>About Mradi</h1>
		<hr>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-4 about-image-holder">
				<!-- <img src="https://www.mradi.co.ke/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Mradi-Logo-156x210.png" alt="Logo for Mradi">-->
				<%= image_tag "mradi-logo-300x300.png", width: 250, alt: "Logo for Mradi"%>
				
				<section class="skills">
					<% @skills.each do |skill| %>
						<div class="skill">
							<h5> <%= skill.title %> </h5>
							<div class="progress" style="height: 20px">
							   <div 
							  	class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-danger progress-bar-animated" 
							  	role="progressbar" 
							  	aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>" 
							  	aria-valuemin="0" 
							  	aria-valuemax="100" 
							  	style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"> <%= skill.percent_utilized %>	
							  	</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					<% end %>
				</section>
			</div>
			
			<div class="col-md-8">
				<p>With over a decade of development experience in a number of industries I realized that the typical product creation process
				between clients and developers was flawed. All to often developers rarely communicate to clients throughout the development stage;
				resulting in a final product that fail sto reach the goal sought by the customer and end user.</p>

				<p>For this reason I decided to utilize a completely different development pattern that focuses on highly focused communication
				and transparent design patterns. When I take on a project; not only do I work to craft the application according to the client specifications, I give daily updates to ensure that the project is aligning properly with the client goals.
				The end result is the right product, delivered on time and on budget.</p>

				<p>
					<button 
						class="btn btn-primary" 
						type="button" 
						data-toggle="collapse" 
						data-target="#jobHistory"
						aria-expanded="false" 
						aria-controller="jobHistory"> Job History 
					</button>
				</p>
				<p>
					<div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
						<div class="card card-block">
							<section>
								<h4> PlainPath Consulting Limited </h4>
								<p> 2018 </p>
							</section>

							
							<section>
								<h5> Responsibilities </h5>
								<ol>
									<li> Redesign their website into a WordPress site </li>
									<li> Manage their mail server and hosting services </li>
								</ol>	
							</section>							
						</div>

						<div class="card card-block">
							<section>
								<h4> The Mahogany Group Limited</h4>
								<p> 2018 </p>
							</section>

							
							<section>
								<h5> Responsibilities </h5>
								<ol>
									<li> Manage a social media app project </li>
								</ol>	
							</section>	
						</div>

						<div class="card card-block">
							<section>
								<h4> Immortal AI </h4>
								<p> 2018 </p>
							</section>

							
							<section>
								<h5> Responsibilities </h5>
								<ol>
									<li> Agile coach as they build a blockchain ICO token </li>
								</ol>	
							</section>	
						</div>
					</div>
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>	
</div>

